v0.3.0 (2013-10-22):
* Ubuntu 13.10 / GNOME 3.8 compatibility:
  * Updated GSettings to monitor / clamp
  * Fixed SIGTERM / SIGINT / SIGHUP handling
  * Listen to signals from ConsoleKit / systemd-logind

v0.2.0 (2013-04-17):
* Disable DPMS (Energy Star) features when inhibiting screensaver
* Added --no-dpms command-line argument to prevent DPMS disabling

v0.1.0 (2012-11-08):
* Initial release
